  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-lg-3 ">
    <div class="thumbnail">
       <div class="palette palette_small palette-firm-dark" >Places To Visit</div>
       <div class="1equalHeights visiting_block">
         <a href="<%= public_page_show_path('Places to visit'.parameterize) -%>"><img src="/assets/placesV2.png" alt="" /></a>
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-15 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
    <p>
      A very warm welcome to Merthyr Tydfil - the largest town in the beautiful Welsh Valleys and well known for its vibrant centre and friendly atmosphere.
      Merthyr Tydfil Town Centre is a great place to visit for shopping, eating and drinking,
      as well as providing a wonderful stepping-stone to the amazing array of attractions and activities on its doorstep.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can find out here all about the shops, cafes, restaurants and professional services that Merthyr Tydfil Town Centre
      has to offer in our easy to use directory. Look out also for a host of special offers and promotions from the
      town’s businesses – you don’t want to miss out on a great discount from a favourite shop or restaurant!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

